Troubleshoot Your Intelligent Apps

To access the logs for your Intelligent App, click the app name and go to the Monitoring tab. The app logs provide details for each installation and task associated with the app.

From Setup, select your app instance and click Monitoring.
Search for a particular event by entering the event value in the Search box.
View the status of the event, and the progress of individual tasks from the Event field.

You can see all tasks associated with an event, details for each task, such as whether it was skipped, successful, or failed, and error messages to help troubleshoot.

If log entries are available, click a task to see the entries. The log entries provide granular detail for each installation and each task.

IMPORTANT: Log detail level is dependent on the log level selected at app creation.

For more information on how to use this page for troubleshooting, see the Use the App Install History Page in the Analytics Templates Developer Guide.
title: Troubleshooting Intelligent Apps
